-- Balda Lowers Forecast, Now Expects Loss as Revenue Falls Short of Target
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-10-15T06:25:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/balda-lowers-forecast-now-expects-loss-as-revenue-falls-short-of-target.html
Balda AG lowered its 2010 forecast,
saying the company will fall “clearly short” of the forecasted
earnings before interest and taxes of about 2.5 million euros.
Ebit is likely to be “negative in the single-digit range,” the
company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
